divs: Sighting Details I was out in my backyard playing with my dog when I noticed this round object in the sky it was a green oval shapr in the middle with a lighter green surrounding it. I probably observed for about 5 minutes then it went off to the south. All the dogs in the area started getting real wierd, lots of pacing my dog got sick just as I went outside before I saw the Object I don t knw if something scared him to be sick or I don t know. The object really didn t do anything but sit there and then went south.
